 - the filename isn't important with this portable program so rename it all you want.


 - this portable program doesn't use a sandbox(temp folder), so if it does ever give
you any trouble, just delete the program itself, make a copy of the ".BACKUP" file,
and rename the copy, removing the .BACKUP from the end of it.


 - this calculator is just like the one that comes with vista except that it can also
do unit conversions.


 - to switch between the calculator and the unit converter, just go to the view menu.


 - the unit converter does areas, energy, lengths, power, pressure, temperatures,
velocity, volume, weight, currency, and engine consumption, although i'm not sure
how useful the last two would be.
